ve to that of the $J/\\psi$. A good fit\nof all RHIC and LHC $J/\\psi$ and $\\psi(2S)$ data, for transverse momenta\n$P_\\perp\\leq 5$ GeV in p+p and p+A collisions, is obtained for $\\Lambda\\sim 10$\nMeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Jul 2017 08:24:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Feb 2018 02:36:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-02"}
