_q}=0$. For the first time, we show\nthat ${B_q}\\ge 2/3$ by explicitly constructing some towers of function fields\nin this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Jul 2017 15:25:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-25"}
